{"tid":1529300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌港鐵前線嘅人係咪根本係冇出過去發夢？","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T20:26:12.000Z","uid":19982,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e911f7eaa6db12a584b2b1888b325df4f2e6d129","tid":1529300,"uid":19982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"根本好多事係高層搞出嚟，有出開去發夢嘅一定有比前線職員幫過：<br />\n<br />\n1. 車長開廣播講香港人加油<br />\n2. 見人跳閘扮追/ 當睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n721：尾班車 直接開閘比示威者過<br />\n728：尾班車 直接開閘比示威者過<br />\n901：太子戮殺列車下一班車長唔理黑警停車直接開車走<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄其他人可以幫手補充<br />\n<br />\n警察直接入控制室/高職拉制前線員工根本冇野做到 可以做嘅都做哂，喺TG放過風都唔敢<strong><ins>以職員身份</ins></strong>開聲 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量破壞狗鐵 前線職員唔洗賠錢冇損失</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 請對準狗鐵高層同股東<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d8fd0e1dff284919e15e1ba28684699309d052b9","tid":1529300,"uid":19982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"［港鐵］你地鐘意屌就屌 但我想大家諗清楚<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528922</a><br />\n<br />\n前線職員辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79f02f1a94ebb3ce8fff8f5ed9b8359bf9ee506","tid":1529300,"uid":199662,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07e19982dca2e35fb9425c9ec01d4ed367d7051","tid":1529300,"uid":84944,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:04:15.000Z","msg":"唔好再講有良心就辭職，交通方面多個照應點都係好事"},{"pid":"b31c3f090ef26bd825fe94e1504dd7d3dc0f7dc9","tid":1529300,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三罷點可以冇不合作運動配合？<br />\n人多想做咩都得</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLJBax4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th